<emph etype = "bold">
B1194: Starting Motor Relay Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Inconsistency between starting motor control relay monitor input voltage and starting motor control relay control condition continuous for longer than specified time.
</ptxt>
</entry>
